title: C'era una volta in Cina 2 (1992) Directed by Tsui Hark

sources.title: C'era una volta in Cina 2 (1992) Directed by Tsui Hark
sources.description:
Arriving by train in Guangzhou, 1895, the trio battles the White Lotus cult, who seek to kill all foreigners, and the pretty, European-clad 13th Aunt. This isn't the last fight for kung fu master Dr. Wong (Jet Li).

Original title: Once Upon a Time in China II
Alternative title: Wong Fei-hung II: Nam yi dong ji keung (黃飛鴻之二 男兒當自強)

Director: Tsui Hark
Writers: Tsui Hark, Tin-suen Chan (Chan Tin-sueng)

Main cast:
Jet Li – Wong Fei-hung
Rosamund Kwan – Aunt Yee (Thirteenth Aunt)
Max Mok – Leung Foon
Donnie Yen – Commander Lan
David Chiang – Luke Ho-dung (Dr. Sun Yat-sen)
Zhang Tielin – Governor
Ji Chunhua – Priest Gao (White Lotus enforcer)
Hung Yan-yan (Xiong Xin-Xin) – Kung (White Lotus fighter)

Genres: Action, Adventure, History
Release date: 1992 (Hong Kong: August 21, 1992)
Filming location: Guangdong, China; Hong Kong
